<p><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;%当青春与艺术碰撞，会迸发出怎样的火花？经济管理学院“Show Time小剧场-青春艺起燃”圆满举行！以“学生主导·多元表达·青春共鸣”为内核，打造沉浸式艺术狂欢，让每个青年都能站上舞台，用艺术点燃青春能量，绽放属于自己的光芒！</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1747297813738.png" alt="1747297813738.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1747297813738.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;"><strong>PART 1</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;"><strong>节目单</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;"><strong>🎤《好想爱这个世界啊》</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;"><strong>温柔的嗓音缓缓流淌</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;"><strong>细腻的情感直击心灵</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;"><strong>每一个音符都诉说着对世界的热爱与期待</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;"><strong>用歌声治愈每一颗年轻的心</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1747297834408.png" alt="1747297834408.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1747297834408.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;"><strong>💃《one spark》</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;"><strong>舞步与心跳共振</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;"><strong>每个卡点都迸发出摄人心魄的力量</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;"><strong>舞台魅力在此刻倾情绽放</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1747297847638.png" alt="1747297847638.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1747297847638.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;"><strong>🎤《十年》</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;"><strong>深情的演唱</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;"><strong>将岁月的故事娓娓道来</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;"><strong>熟悉的旋律勾起回忆</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;"><strong>在歌声中感受时光的流转与成长的感悟</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1747297858571.png" alt="1747297858571.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1747297858571.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;"><strong>🎹《The Truth That You Leave》</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;"><strong>优美的旋律流淌</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;"><strong>指尖在琴键上舞动</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;"><strong>奏响一曲动人乐章</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1747297869803.png" alt="1747297869803.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1747297869803.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;"><strong>🎤《于是》</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;"><strong>独特的嗓音</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;"><strong>富有感染力的演唱</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;"><strong>用歌声诠释内心的情感</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;"><strong>带你走进一场音乐的心灵之旅</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1747297880691.png" alt="1747297880691.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1747297880691.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;"><strong>🎤《永不失联的爱》</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;"><strong>温暖的歌声</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;"><strong>传递着坚定的爱意</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;"><strong>每一个音符都充满力量</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;"><strong>诉说着对爱的执着与坚守</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1747297894656.png" alt="1747297894656.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1747297894656.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;"><strong>💃《如愿》</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;"><strong>优美的舞姿</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;"><strong>舒缓的节奏</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;"><strong>舞者们用肢体语言演绎美好</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;"><strong>带来一场视觉与情感的双重盛宴</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1747297911620.png" alt="1747297911620.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1747297911620.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;当最后一个音符消散在礼堂上空，当舞台灯光渐渐暗下，经济管理学院“Show Time小剧场-青春艺起燃”在热烈的掌声与欢呼声中圆满落下帷幕。此次活动不仅展现了经管学子的多才多艺，更搭建起一个自由表达与交流的平台，让青春在艺术的舞台上尽情绽放。期待下一个舞台我们再见！</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1747297931411.png" alt="1747297931411.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1747297931411.png" style="width: 50%;"></p>